{"tid":1638011,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【新疆解放軍抽獎】樹葉、石頭、樹枝當獎品 內地網民：太有意義了","createTime":"2019-10-08T07:20:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T10:57:18.000Z","uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"eae472edff4203ced97011c083bcc3fc54c9f8f5","tid":1638011,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:20:34.000Z","msg":"即時兩岸<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191007/large/1570435498_4f07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191007%2Flarge%2F1570435498_4f07.jpg&h=70709f85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n解放軍新疆軍區周日（6日）開通官方微博@喀喇昆侖衞士，隨後發佈抽獎帖文，稱獎品清單是「史上最硬核（意指勁揪）」，獎品是樹葉、石頭、樹枝、祝福卡。不過，微博下所見的，卻是一群人表示「特別有意義」。<br />\n<br />\n獎品清單包括小白楊哨所的樹葉、阿拉山口的石頭、三十里營房的紅柳木、可可托海邊防連的祝福錦囊、神仙灣哨所的一捧土、鐵列克提邊防連的刀山石、「進藏先遺英雄連」官兵的祝福卡、河尾灘邊防連的一頁塊石頭。<br />\n<br />\n看到這份清單，竟獲內地網民盛讚「太有意義了吧，有心了」、「這是真正千金難買的禮物」，甚至有人留言「不要快遞（速遞）要兵哥哥親自送來」。<br />\n<br />\n至於誰有幸獲得樹葉、石頭、樹枝等心意，當局將於12日下午6時揭曉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191007/60126694\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191007%2F60126694&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNkBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=8efb9e88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191007%2F60126694&h=f52c14e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191007/60126694</a>"},{"pid":"011ecee1fbc75827ea2a9419f19786f691d49943","tid":1638011,"uid":284304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:21:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/daa/1eb/daa1eb716a70be54e618859dda7f2bd4e42cde71_n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2Fdaa%2F1eb%2Fdaa1eb716a70be54e618859dda7f2bd4e42cde71_n.png&h=6f1f8fcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n塊葉係咁用"},{"pid":"8ad08bb5db44d5f7116f6817c7946ba9a92ea3d6","tid":1638011,"uid":55563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:21:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8279e3779adc0b91b450c77650d11403a6a4ee9f","tid":1638011,"uid":275370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:25:22.000Z","msg":"鳩毛都可以做獎品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aaccfad27c3ace0067a3686e5c1a61ad5fe8ff6","tid":1638011,"uid":313676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:26:29.000Z","msg":"jm9"},{"pid":"1b1c6d017e5afce935d6370469697e57bad0f22f","tid":1638011,"uid":288312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:32:13.000Z","msg":"請幫手推爆黑警散布謠言, 推到佢四點鐘又口啞啞!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n［極醜惡又一例證］香港警察又掩埋真相 鼓吹謠言散播<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1636039\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1636039</a>"},{"pid":"2821d1215bc40d1ef70bdd67bc3f00844e590396","tid":1638011,"uid":46943,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:51:31.000Z","msg":"非洲豬瘟豬尾一條<br />\n光頭神探精液套一個<br />\n豆腐渣建築碎片一塊"},{"pid":"d205b1a15f4418727477bd5c3681caf9f8caff36","tid":1638011,"uid":9136,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2821d1215bc40d1ef70bdd67bc3f00844e590396","tid":1638011,"uid":46943,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:51:31.000Z","msg":"非洲豬瘟豬尾一條<br />\n光頭神探精液套一個<br />\n豆腐渣建築碎片一塊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:05:34.000Z","msg":"三聚氰氨奶粉一罐<br />\n假三文魚連蟲50件"},{"pid":"1c0fadb5b925db4a036acb03285a69896c81ba32","tid":1638011,"uid":188334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08